le="Ration Wasser"><img alt="Ration Wasser" src="/wiki/images/8/80/Wasserration.gif" width="16" height="16" border="0" /></a></span>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nPreprocessor node count: 156/1000000\nPost-expand include size: 2841/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 469/2097152 bytes\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key nmelzer_mysqldfc6c114020d400ab7856ec4cc232b58:pcache:idhash:1129-0!1!0!!de!2 and timestamp 20100831195637 -->\n', '{{IngameText|Eine furchterregende Waffe, die nur noch etwas reines Wasser benÃ¶tigt.}}\n\n== Kombinationen ==\n \n{{Item|Aqua-Splash (5 Ladungen)}}= {{Item|Aqua-Splash (leer)|kurz=1}} + {{Item|Ration Wasser|kurz=1}}\n\n\n[[Kategorie:Gegenstand]]\n');
